{{DISPLAYTITLE:OFIELD_A}}{{TAGDEF|OFIELD_A|[real]}}

Description: The tag {{TAG|OFIELD_A}} sets the desired order parameter <math>Q_6</math> in the [[:Category:Interface pinning|Interface pinning]] method.
----
The bias potential in the [[:Category:Interface pinning|Interface pinning]] method is written as
::<math>U_\text{bias}(\mathbf{R}) = \frac\kappa2 \left(Q_6(\mathbf{R}) - A\right)^2 </math>.
The tag {{TAG|OFIELD_A}} sets the desired value of the order parameter <math>A</math>.

